[b][size=120]Want to try this awesomeness?[/size][/b]


[font=Courier New][size=120][b][code]-Download the ROM and GApps of your choice
-Backup each and every partition from TWRP Recovery
-Make a full wipe (system, data, cache, dalvik)
-Install AEX Package
-Install GAPPS package
-Wipe cache!
-And at last Reboot!
[First boot will take few minutes! Have patience]
Clean Flash is always recommended![/code][/b][/size][/font]


[img]http://i.imgur.com/mmK3YNQ.png[/img]


